where the real jade pendants are.

38
00:01:59,780 --> 00:02:00,300
Out with it.

39
00:02:00,820 --> 00:02:01,820
Where are the real jade pendants?

40
00:02:02,140 --> 00:02:02,500
Yes.

41
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:04,020
I put the real jade pendants there.

42
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:06,020
I'm the only survivor in the Lin family.

43
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:07,580
Naturally, the real ones are with me.

44
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:09,340
My patience has a limit.

45
00:02:09,700 --> 00:02:10,140
Tell me.

46
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:11,900
Where are the real jade pendants?

47
00:02:12,620 --> 00:02:14,060
I will never give them to you,
even if I die!

48
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:15,220
