49
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:16,980
Chief.

50
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:37,340
Qingming.

51
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:39,540
This poison pill

52
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,500
will give her excruciating pain

53
00:02:42,020 --> 00:02:43,540
and make her want to kill herself.

54
00:02:43,900 --> 00:02:45,060
Take her out

55
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:46,700
and find the jade pendants,

56
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:49,460
then kill her.

57
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:50,580
Yes.

58
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:51,700
Move!

59
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:53,580
Move!

60
