Please hold on, Mengchen.

63
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:07,500
Zeyu has gone to find the antidote.

64
00:03:08,260 --> 00:03:09,340
You must hold on.

65
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:12,940
Why did you...

66
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:14,980
Why did you kill Mr. Cao?

67
