73
00:03:54,220 --> 00:03:58,060
I smell the scent of osmanthus oil
Young Lady smears.

74
00:03:58,420 --> 00:03:59,460
Young Lady?

75
00:04:00,260 --> 00:04:02,300
Mengchen isn't your daughter?

76
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:05,660
What a cruel twist of fate.

77
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:08,380
Young Lady was kidnapped
by human traffickers back then.

78
00:04:10,540 --> 00:04:12,540
My daughter, Cao Mengchen,

79
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:15,260
was mistaken for the daughter of
the Lin family

80
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:17,260
and was killed during the massacre.

81
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:22,140
The present Mengchen

82
00:04:22,820 --> 00:04:23,620
is

83
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:26,060
the surviving daughter of
the Lin family,

84
00:04:26,780 --> 00:04:27,780
Lin Yueniang.

85
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:35,460
I can't believe
only your side of the story.

86
00:04:35,860 --> 00:04:38,020
Someone witnessed you killed Jingzhe.

87
00:04:38,140 --> 00:04:39,100
How do you explain this?

88
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:41,180
I never killed anyone.

89
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:43,420
