of revenge.

93
00:04:55,180 --> 00:04:56,060
It is time

94
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:57,820
to bring the truth to light

95
00:04:58,220 --> 00:04:59,900
and for the dust to settle.

96
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:11,620
Ye Xiaosheng.

97
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:14,700
Kill me.

98
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:20,420
And Blood Sacrifice Gang will
believe the jade pendants and you.

99
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:22,900
I can't.

100
00:05:24,780 --> 00:05:28,380
You are the only family Mengchen has.

101
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:30,020
You are my family too.

102
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:32,660
Let's come up with a way.

103
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:34,420
There must be a good way.

104
00:05:40,180 --> 00:05:41,020
Mr. Cao.

105
00:05:41,220 --> 00:05:42,060
Mr. Cao.

106
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:43,700
