107
00:05:51,020 --> 00:05:51,820
Are you all right?

108
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,300
I didn't expect

109
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:03,420
Zhou Yuan'an to be the mastermind.

110
00:06:03,980 --> 00:06:06,060
I was forced to bring you
to the Blood Sacrifice Gang.

111
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:07,620
But before we went,

112
00:06:07,980 --> 00:06:10,660
I have already prepared the antidote
to the Heart-burning Powder.

113
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:13,620
It contains

114
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:16,020
substances that could cause
nervous disorder.

115
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,340
Is there any antidote to this?

116
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:20,980
No.

117
00:06:22,260 --> 00:06:24,540
However, there are
some sedative medications

118
00:06:25,100 --> 00:06:27,540
that can counterattack the effects of
nervous disorder.

119
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:28,540
Get it for me.

120
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:29,340
Just in case anything happens.

121
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:30,780
I don't want Mengchen

122
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:32,300
to be in danger again.

123
00:06:33,580 --> 00:06:34,420
All right.

124
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:48,500
But I didn't expect Zhou Yuan'an
to feed you the poison pill.

125
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:51,100
Mengchen.

126
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:52,700
Mengchen.

127
