It is not your fault.

128
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:57,260
Joining the Blood Sacrifice Gang

129
00:06:58,180 --> 00:07:00,140
or investigating
the Lin family massacre case

130
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:02,340
are my own choices.

131
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:05,020
But, Brother,

132
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:09,100
I feel so terrible.

133
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:10,700
Mengchen, Mengchen.

134
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:12,180
You must hang in there.

135
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:12,980
Believe me.

136
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:14,020
You must hang in there,

137
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:14,740
Mengchen.

138
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:16,340
Believe me.

139
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:18,620
Once everything is over,

140
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:20,020
